sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/GitOps
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Manager as Controller Manager<br/>Leader-elected Pod
    participant Renderer as Manifest Engine<br/>Kustomize/Helm
    participant OLM as Operator Lifecycle Manager<br/>Subscription CRDs
    participant CompOp as Component Operator<br/>e.g., KServe

    Note over User,CompOp: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation & Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST DataScienceCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>Kubernetes API auth
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response<br/>(Allow/Deny)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>Kubernetes API auth
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated DSC resource
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created confirmation

    Note over Manager: Watch event triggered

    Manager->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>Service account token
    K8sAPI-->>Manager: DSC resource spec

    Manager->>Renderer: Render component manifests<br/>In-process call
    Renderer-->>Manager: Rendered YAML manifests

    Manager->>K8sAPI: CREATE/UPDATE resources<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>Service account token
    Note right of Manager: Creates Deployments,<br/>Services, ConfigMaps,<br/>Secrets, etc.

    Note over User,CompOp: Flow 2: Component Deployment via OLM

    Manager->>K8sAPI: CREATE Subscription<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>Service account token
    Note right of Manager: operators.coreos.com/v1alpha1

    K8sAPI-->>Manager: Subscription created

    OLM->>K8sAPI: Watch Subscription<br/>Internal cluster event
    OLM->>K8sAPI: CREATE CSV, Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>OLM service account

    Note over CompOp: Component operator starts

    CompOp->>K8sAPI: Watch component CRDs<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>Component service account
    CompOp->>K8sAPI: Reconcile component resources<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS

    Note over User,CompOp: Flow 3: Webhook Validation Flow

    User->>K8sAPI: POST DSCInitialization CR<br/>Auth: User credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS<br/>Kubernetes API auth
    Note right of Webhook: Validates AdminGroups<br/>(cannot contain 'system:authenticated')
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: ValidationResponse<br/>Allowed: true/false
    alt Validation fails
        K8sAPI-->>User: 403 Forbidden<br/>Admission webhook denied
    else Validation succeeds
        K8sAPI-->>User: 201 Created
    end

    Note over User,CompOp: Flow 4: Component Management State Change

    User->>K8sAPI: PATCH DataScienceCluster<br/>.spec.components.kserve.managementState="Removed"
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
    K8sAPI-->>User: DSC updated

    Manager->>K8sAPI: Watch event received<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS
    Manager->>K8sAPI: DELETE KServe resources<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS<br/>Service account token
    Note right of Manager: Removes Subscription,<br/>Deployments, Services

    K8sAPI-->>Manager: Resources deleted
    Manager->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DSC status<br/>HTTPS/443 mTLS
    Note right of Manager: Status: Removed
